@ProspectId uniqueiden..er, @ProspectDisposi.onId int, @UpdatedBy uniqueiden..er
AS BEGIN
UPDATE USMC.Prospect SET ProspectDisposi.onId = @ProspectDisposi.onId, LastUpdateDate = GetDate(), LastUpdateUserId = @UpdatedBy WHERE ProspectId = @ProspectId
END
